  "title": "Audit Associate | Degree | Nicoll Highway | 5 Days | Up To $3.5K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Audit Associate</strong><br />Salary: Up to $3500<br />Working Days: 5 days / 5.5 days (Saturday half day during peak period)<br />Working Hours: 8:30am - 5:30pm<br />Working Location: Golden Mile Tower (Nicoll Highway MRT)</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Undertakes specific stages of audit work under supervision.</li><li>Appreciate the underlying principles behind the tasks assigned as part of the audit plan.</li><li>Able to make adjustments to the application of skills to improve the work tasks or solve non-complex issues.</li><li>Able to build relationships, work in a team and identify ethical issues with reference to the code of professional conduct and ethics.</li><li>Select and apply from a range of known solutions to familiar problems and takes responsibility for own learning and performance.</li><li>Work with any of the assurance teams to obtain an understanding of our client’s business.</li><li>Develop an audit plan/strategy for an audit of financial statements and document the planning procedures.</li><li>Prepare/tailor audit programmes based on areas of audit emphasis determined at the planning stage.</li><li>Perform audit tests of controls and substantive procedures based on planned audit approach to address the various assertions, eg: existence & completeness, rights and obligations, valuation, accuracy, presentation and disclosure.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree or equivalent</li><li>1-2 year of working experience as audit associate.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong> </p>",
